author: John Bowden
title: State Dept. says it has repatriated 9,000 Americans amid coronavirus outbreak
description: The State Department announced Tuesday that it had repatriated more than 9,000 American citizens amid the ongoing global coronavirus outbreak....
content:
The State Department announced Tuesday that it had repatriated more than 9,000 U.S. citizens who were stranded abroad as a result of the coronavirus pandemic.
